    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147560/extras/212619b2cb8be30007b72e39eb91e365.avif?t=1756379461\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep within a mysterious grove, you uncover a hidden clearing - its heart filled with strange machines and ancient alien ruins. As you investigate, the dormant technology awakens, and in a flash, you're thrust into a distant, otherworldly realm. Surrounded by the unfamiliar, you must unravel the mysteries of this alien world and find your way back - if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147560/extras/6ac3be6349199ec999d23b95944d1e57.avif?t=1756379461\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, discover, solve, and progress through this alien world to uncover its secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147560/extras/c8380a95f174c4f17977f03022ec44c9.avif?t=1756379461\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lands of XON is a first-person puzzle and exploration game set in the remnants of a lost alien civilization. Uncover the purpose of ancient machines, decipher forgotten technology, and piece together the story of a world long abandoned. As you explore its vast, enigmatic landscapes, you'll need to solve its secrets - not just to understand what happened here, but to find your way back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147560/extras/5e3ea48478954f91eb4b1a18e7fa0033.avif?t=1756379461\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p>",
